<hymn_number>293</hymn_number>
<title>nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma 迦南293</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma? nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma?
 nǐ yī dìng yào qiáng liú tā hé tā shuō shuō xīn lǐ huà.
 nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma? nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma?
 tiān sè yǐ wǎn kuài bǎ tā jiē huí nǐ de jiā.
 cóng gǔ dào jīn yǒu duō shǎo yù jiàn zhǔ de rén,
 gān yuàn bèi shàng shí zì jià bǎ yī qiè dōu shě xià
 nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma? nǐ yù jiàn zhǔ le ma?
 bù yào zài jù jué, bù yào zài chén mò, yī dìng yào gēn zhe tā.</lyrics>
</song>